Strong presence of Italian publishers at the Frankfurt International Book Fair.
More than 300 Italian publishers present at the 60th edition of the Buchmesse, the most important international meeting in the exchange of rights.
The Frankfurt International Book Fair awaits for this edition, more than 7 thousand exhibitors from 101 different countries who will occupy the 171.790 square meters of the Fair with more than 403 thousand titles in exhibition, and Turkey as guest of honor.
